Bella won her first match and is pretty cocky about it. She loves the action, the physicality of the matches and excitedly loves fucking the loser.
Annie Cruz is undefeated this season - words a lot of you thought you would never read. Annie has improved and her drive and energy on the mat is unsurpassed by any wrestler. When Annie is on the mat she brings it from whistle to whistle.
This is a great un-scripted wrestling war. The loser ends up getting ass fucked, hard, and made to squirt all over the mat. The winner then wipes the mat with the loser.
title: Bella Rossi "The Annihilator"(1-0)
